1057
01:27:36,039 --> 01:27:37,343
Cedric.

1058
01:27:40,653 --> 01:27:43,142
Buatlah. Bukalah.

1059
01:27:51,493 --> 01:27:56,517
<i>Carilah di mana suara kami muncul</i>

1060
01:27:56,602 --> 01:28:01,276
<i>Kami tak boleh menyanyi
di dasar timbul</i>

1061
01:28:01,361 --> 01:28:06,002
<i>Ada satu jam untuk mencari</i>

1062
01:28:06,530 --> 01:28:11,199
<i>Untuk cari apa yang kami miliki</i>

1063
01:28:19,332 --> 01:28:20,808
