susun semula bukunya?

1088
01:30:03,833 --> 01:30:05,914
Kalau awak berminat dengan
tumbuh-tumbuhan,...

1089
01:30:06,025 --> 01:30:08,833
...awak patut baca buku
"Panduan Herbologi Goshawk".

1090
01:30:09,328 --> 01:30:13,732
