1103
01:30:45,678 --> 01:30:47,515
-Ada taruhan?
-Taruhan Fleur, 10-1.

1104
01:30:49,748 --> 01:30:51,538
-Awak pasti tentangnya, Neville?
-Sudah tentulah.

1105
01:30:51,623 --> 01:30:53,526
-Selama sejam?
